{"tid":1761891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「孩子不要催淚彈」親子集會及小型遊行 12月1日，星期日10:00 愛丁堡廣場  歡迎一家大細去","createTime":"2019-11-29T07:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T15:10:19.000Z","uid":179775,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cb5909a1681d2dab69051285d0fd30640dd780b2","tid":1761891,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:57:35.000Z","msg":"「孩子不要催淚彈」親子集會及小型遊行 詳細內容<br />\n***今早已獲不反對通知書***<br />\n日期：12月1日，星期日<br />\n<br />\n時間表及遊行路線:<br />\n10:00-10:30am<br />\n愛丁堡廣場大會堂低座對出空地集會<br />\n集會內容~<br />\n1. 受催淚彈影響有身體反應的家長分享。<br />\n2. 醫生分享、律師分享、社工分享。<br />\n3. 孩子們畫畫，表達對催淚彈的感受。<br />\n<br />\n10:30-11:15am<br />\n遊行~<br />\n愛丁堡廣場大會堂低座對出空地(起點) &gt; 龍和道南面行人路 &gt; 橫過龍和道 &gt; 龍和道北面行人路 &gt; 橫過耀星街 &gt; 龍和道北面行人路 &gt; 添馬公園 &gt; 夏𢡱道天橋 &gt; 夏𢡱道北面行人路 &gt; 添美道西面行人路 &gt; 政府總部東翼前地外添美道西面行人路指定公眾活動區（終點)<br />\n<br />\n11:15-11:45am<br />\n到達政府總部東翼前地外添美道西面行人路指定公眾活動區，孩子貼圖畫後解散。<br />\n<br />\n目的：<br />\n向政府和社會表達家長們對孩子健康受催淚彈影響的擔心<br />\n<br />\n**暫時有3位候任區議員會出席支持，請家長繼續幫忙邀請各區候任區議員出席。<br />\n<br />\n備註：<br />\n1. 每個家庭自備所需的畫紙、顏色，以及製作所需的道具。<br />\n2. 如擔心孩子在場會吸到催淚彈殘留物，請自備有關裝備，例如：口罩、豬咀、帽子、長衫、眼罩、以及盡量遮蓋所有外露的皮膚。**但警方負責人對社工爸媽說蒙面法仍然生效，家長自行決定和判斷。<br />\n3. 如真的非常擔心，就請家長不帶孩子參與；社工爸媽孩子較大，所以會帶同出席集會，孩子也需要為自己的健康發聲。<br />\n4. 當日會派發50個氦氣球給孩子遊行時拿著，請有汽球的家長幫孩子用重物綁住繩尾，以防飛走。<br />\n<br />\n主辦單位: 社工爸媽自家教（江承昌 謝麗敏)<br />\n聯絡電話: 95651040"},{"pid":"743fa05fc6f11ea70f7bec4d194aee26e7fe4005","tid":1761891,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ad04fe4f4e26c592b852af6d71679ab673f82e","tid":1761891,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48329903d67a2b1c7c52df989691f95fccb66cc5","tid":1761891,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:07:17.000Z","msg":"deadline fighter 一齊寫聖誕卡畀英國歐洲議員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1761460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1761460</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n拉落去有哂英國address <br />\n依幾日截郵<br />\n幫手寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a7eb9e6dcb4e2501f78b2b0933bebba3fb61b1","tid":1761891,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa59b06994d944f3fd4ec260eee7c9f850a1ed0","tid":1761891,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWemmrP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWemmrP.jpg&h=50a0c385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>運動未完 仍需努力</strong></span>"},{"pid":"80271671491045f50e71dcd90fad53f3acb3e349","tid":1761891,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T14:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f632ca4d6c69ab19